                                        2970
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Panoramic image datasets. We used three large- scale datasets of outdoor panoramas, the StreetLearn dataset [38], the SP360 dataset [9], and the HoliCity dataset [64], as listed in Table 3. In StreetLearn, we used the Manhattan"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
