                                        2272,
                                        798
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " because the height of a camera mounted on a car is sufficiently small with respect to the distance between the camera and other objects. The horizontal center of the panoramic images corresponds with the travel direction of cars: the pan angle is "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
