                                        2272,
                                        2118
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Vanishing- point label ambiguity. As shown in Table 2, we annotated the VP/ADPs of the image coordinates and labels on the basis of panoramic- image width and height. We found that some generated fisheye images had label ambiguity; that is, we cannot annotate unique VP/ADP labels for these images. For example, we cannot distinguish one image with a "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        1282,
                                        1570,
                                        2272,
                                        2118
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "0^{\\circ}"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        1282,
                                        1570,
                                        2272,
                                        2118
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "- pan angle from another with a "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        1282,
                                        1570,
                                        2272,
                                        2118
                                    ],
                                    "type": "inline_equation",
                                    "content": "180^{\\circ}"
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        1282,
                                        1570,
                                        2272,
                                        2118
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "- pan angle because we cannot determine the direction of travel of the cars from one image. In other words, we cannot distinguish front labels from back labels in Table 2. Similarly, we cannot distinguish left labels from right labels."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
                    "index": 13
