                                        2272,
                                        2468
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Removal of label ambiguity. Considering generalized cases of label ambiguity, we annotated the image coordinates of VP/ADPs as follows. We "
                                },
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        1282,
                                        2125,
                                        2272,
                                        2468
