                                        1282,
                                        2125,
                                        2272,
                                        2468
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "- rotationally align all labels based on two conditions: 1) the images have back labels without front labels, and 2) the images have right labels without front and left labels. Details of the number of labels can be found in the supplementary materials."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
